<div class="section" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
  <h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;color:#e5e7eb;">Platform</h3>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Does max open trades guarantee all slots are filled?</strong><br>No. It sets an upper limit. Filters and cooldown can still block entries.</div>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Why does a trade close quickly?</strong><br>Price can hit stop-loss before management rules activate.</div>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Are backtest results guaranteed live?</strong><br>No. Backtests are simulated and do not predict future results.</div>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Can the bot miss entries/exits?</strong><br>Yes. Exchange/API latency, outages, market gaps, or data delays can affect execution.</div>
</div>

<div class="section" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
