  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Is this financial advice?</strong><br>No. AlphaConfluence provides software and educational information only.</div>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Who is responsible for settings?</strong><br>You are responsible for your configuration, risk controls, and final execution decisions.</div>
  <div class="journal-entry"><strong>Can I lose money?</strong><br>Yes. Trading involves substantial risk, including rapid losses in volatile markets.</div>
</div>

